## Entry Point
- `main()` — async `#[tokio::main]`
  - Calls `setup_logging()`
  - Delegates to `grok_cli::cli::app::run()`

## Logging — `setup_logging()`
- Log File: `~/.grok/logs/grok-errors.log` (with graceful fallback)
- Uses `tracing` + `tracing-subscriber`
- Dual sink: coloured stderr + JSON file
- Respects `RUST_LOG`

## Key Modules Loaded Early
- Full crate via `lib.rs`
- CLI app, engine, tools registry, context, safety, etc.

## Recent Notes
- Build system cleaned up: `build.rs` no longer auto-runs markmap generation on every build (avoids repeated warnings).
- To regenerate diagrams: `.\scripts\build-markmaps.ps1`

## Dependencies
- `tokio`, `tracing`, `tracing-subscriber`, `anyhow`, `dirs`

## Error Handling
- Graceful degradation on logging init failure
- `main()` returns `anyhow::Result<()>`

## Notes
- This is the bootstrap. Real behavior lives in `cli/`, `engine/`, `acp/`, and the tool system.